ENTRY       EC 4.1.2.11                 Enzyme
NAME        hydroxymandelonitrile lyase;
            hydroxynitrile lyase;
            oxynitrilase;
            Sorghum hydroxynitrile lyase;
            (S)-4-hydroxymandelonitrile hydroxybenzaldehyde-lyase
CLASS       Lyases;
            Carbon-carbon lyases;
            Aldehyde-lyases
SYSNAME     (S)-4-hydroxymandelonitrile 4-hydroxybenzaldehyde-lyase (cyanide-forming)
REACTION    (S)-4-hydroxymandelonitrile = cyanide + 4-hydroxybenzaldehyde [RN:R02676]
ALL_REAC    R02676;
            (other) R01409 R02811
SUBSTRATE   (S)-4-hydroxymandelonitrile [CPD:C03742]
PRODUCT     cyanide [CPD:C00177];
            4-hydroxybenzaldehyde [CPD:C00633]
COMMENT     Does not accept aliphatic hydroxynitriles, unlike EC 4.1.2.10 (mandelonitrile lyase), EC 4.1.2.46 [aliphatic (R)-hydroxynitrile lyase] and EC 4.1.2.47 [(S)-hydroxynitrile ketone-lyase (cyanide forming)].
